add_box_object.name: add_box_object
add_box_object.description: Makes a box object with given initial position, rotation, velocity, size and add it to the world.

add_circle_object.name: add_circle_object
add_circle_object.description: Makes a circle object with given initial position, rotation, velocity, radius and add it to the world.

add_triangle_object.name: add_triangle_object
add_triangle_object.description: Makes a triangle object with given initial position, rotation, velocity, base, height and add it to the world.

add_vector.name: add_vector
add_vector.description: Adds two vectors together and returns the resultant vector.

add_wall.name: add_wall
add_wall.description: Makes a wall (static box object with no velocity).

apply_force.name: apply_force
apply_force.description: Apllies force to given object at given world point.

apply_force_to_center.name: apply_force_to_center
apply_force_to_center.description: Applies a force to given object at its center.

array_to_vector.name: array_to_vector
array_to_vector.description: Converts an array of 2 numbers into a 2d vector.

get_angular_velocity.name: get_angular_velocity
get_angular_velocity.description: Gets angular velocity of the object at current world time.

get_position.name: get_position
get_position.description: Gets position of the object at current world time.

get_rotation.name: get_rotation
get_rotation.description: Gets rotation of the object at current world time.

get_velocity.name: get_velocity
get_velocity.description: Gets velocity of the object at current world time.

impact_start_time.name: impact_start_time
impact_start_time.description: Gets the impact start time of two currently touching objects. Returns -1 if they are not touching.

is_touching.name: is_touching
is_touching.description: Checks if two objects are touching at current world time.

make_force.name: make_force
make_force.description: Makes a force with direction vector, magnitude, force duration and start time.

make_ground.name: make_ground
make_ground.description: Makes the ground body of the world.

make_vector.name: make_vector
make_vector.description: Makes a 2d vector with the given x and y components.

scale_size.name: scale_size
scale_size.description: Resizes the object with given scale factor.

set_angular_velocity.name: set_angular_velocity
set_angular_velocity.description: Sets current angular velocity of the object.

set_friction.name: set_friction
set_friction.description: Sets the friction value of the object.

set_gravity.name: set_gravity
set_gravity.description: Creates a new physics world and sets the gravity of the world.

subtract_vector.name: subtract_vector
subtract_vector.description: Subtract the second vector from the first and returns the resultant vector.

update_world.name: update_world
update_world.description: Updates the world once with the given time step.
